<collectingRegion id="499AF83D2E14FFF3D6392FB96FC7C4F7" box="[616,743,1508,1531]" country="United States of America" name="Tennessee" pageId="47" pageNumber="46">Tennessee</collectingRegion>
(Map 3).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BE136DF2E14FFF3D4912C7E6E6FC730" blockId="47.[192,847,1571,1596]" box="[192,847,1571,1596]" pageId="47" pageNumber="46">
<emphasis id="B92AEACD2E14FFF3D4912C7E6CB5C737" bold="true" box="[192,405,1571,1595]" pageId="47" pageNumber="46">Natural history</emphasis>
. The specimen was collected in May.
</paragraph>
